            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Malaysia Heritage Studios in Melaka"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Welcome to Malaysia Heritage Studios, the pioneering magical heritage park in Malaysia! Immerse yourself in 13 captivating themes that brilliantly showcase the vibrant colors of Malaysia's rich heritage. Our unique experience transcends traditional museum learning, offering an enchanting journey through arts, architecture, nature, culture, history, and untold legends."
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.3,
        "rating_count": 100
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Walk through the corridors of time and witness history come alive."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Discover the magic woven into every detail as you embark on an enchanting adventure through the heart of Malaysia's cultural legacy."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Join us in celebrating Malaysia's heritage in a way that captures the imagination and touches the heart."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Step into a realm where arts, architecture, nature, culture, history, and untold legends converge in a mesmerizing and immersive experience."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Cultural Showcase: Explore various exhibits that showcase Malaysia’s diverse cultural heritage, including traditional costumes, musical instruments, and artifacts from different ethnic groups.Historical Artifacts: View an extensive collection of historical artifacts that provide insights into Malaysia’s rich history, from ancient times to the colonial era and beyond.Cultural Performances: Enjoy captivating performances of traditional dances, music, and theater. These performances bring to life the vibrant cultural traditions of Malaysia.Ethnic Studios: Explore themed studios dedicated to different ethnic groups in Malaysia, including Malay, Chinese, Indian, and Indigenous communities. Each studio offers a deep dive into the unique customs, traditions, and lifestyles of these communities.Craft Workshops: Participate in hands-on workshops where you can create your own traditional crafts, such as batik prints, beaded jewelry, or woven baskets.Guided Tours: Join guided heritage walks around the studio complex and its surroundings. Knowledgeable guides provide in-depth commentary on the historical and cultural significance of various sites and exhibits.Children’s Corner: A dedicated area for children with interactive games, storytelling sessions, and craft activities designed to educate and entertain young visitors.Cultural Souvenirs: Visit the souvenir shop to purchase unique cultural items and handicrafts, allowing you to take home a piece of Malaysia’s heritage."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Photography may be restricted in certain areas. Pay attention to signs and instructions from staff regarding photography."
